# Game Summary Feature Rules

## Spec Reference
Always refer to the game summary spec: @specs/features/game-summary.md

## Key Requirements
- Full box score per FIBA format
- All player statistics displayed
- Play-by-play log with filtering
- Edit/delete any recorded event
- Export to PDF/CSV

## Components
- `BoxScoreTable` - Standard FIBA box score format
- `TeamComparisonCard` - Side-by-side team stats
- `PlayByPlayList` - Filterable game log
- `AdvancedStatsCard` - FIBA Appendix C stats
- `ExportOptions` - PDF/CSV export

## FIBA Calculations (Appendix C)

### Efficiency Rating (C.K)
```
EFF = PTS - (FGA-FGM) - (FTA-FTM) + REB + AST - TO + ST + BS
```

### Plus/Minus (C.L)
Net points scored while player on court.

### Minutes Rounding (C.A)
- < 30 sec → round down
- >= 30 sec → round up
- > 0 but < 1 min → show 1 min
- 39 min → always round down

## Box Score Columns
#, Player, MIN, PTS, FG, 3PT, FT, REB (O-D), AST, STL, BLK, TO, PF, +/-

## Team Stats (Appendix C)
- Points in Paint
- Fast Break Points
- Second Chance Points
- Points off Turnovers
- Bench Points
- Lead Changes
- Times Tied
- Largest Lead
- Largest Scoring Run
